In [30]:
scores=df['total_run']
scoring=counter(scores)
scoring_zone=[]
keys=[]
for (key,value) in scoring.items():
    scoring_zone.append(value)
    keys.append(key)
print(keys)
plt.pie(scoring_zone,labels=keys,autopct='%1.1f%%',explode=[0,0,0,0,0.35,0.3,0,0.8],shadow=True)
